<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Elsbeth und Hans Streber</head><p>Der Rat bestellt die Adressaten zu einer Besprechung in das Rathaus ein.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_50" id="24v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_50_r2l26"><expan>Elſpete<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Streb<ex>er</ex>ın</expan> vnd Hanſen <expan>Streb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> Sun </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_50_r2l27"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> fruntſchaft beuor / Wir heiſʒen vnd <expan>gepıet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew / bey <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_50_r2l28">eiden / als Jr vns geſworn habt / daʒ Jr nicht laſſet / Jr ſeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_50_r2l29">auf den nehſten freÿtag cʒü Rat cʒeıt / <expan>hynne<ex>n</ex></expan> beÿ vns auf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_50_r2l30">dem Rathaws / wan vvir mit ew cʒereden <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııj̃ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_50_r2l31"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>Mart<ex>in</ex>ı</expan> . </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_50" id="24v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Elspete<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Streb<ex>er</ex>in</expan> und Hansen
                        <expan>Streb<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>ire<ex>m</ex></expan> sun </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> fruntschaft bevor. Wir
                                                heiszen und <expan>gepiet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew bey
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> eiden, als ir uns
                                                gesworn habt, daz ir nicht lasset, ir seit auf den
                                          <app><note><q type="date">nehsten freytag</q>15.11.1409</note></app> czü rat czeit
                                                  <expan>hynne<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns auf dem
                                                rathaws, wan wir mit ew czereden
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>Mart<ex>in</ex>i</expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
